{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": -140,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "# SEO Pipeline — Phase Overview"
    },

    {
      "id": "phase1-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -40,
      "y": -40,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 180,
      "label": "Phase 1 — Signal Collection",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 10,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "**A2 — Entity Extraction** (daily 6:30 AM)\nNews → Sonnet 4.6 → entities\n→ `topic_clusters` + `keywords`"
    },
    {
      "id": "h",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 10,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "**H — GSC Export**\nSearch Console → 7-day CSV\n→ `gsc-exports/latest.csv`"
    },

    {
      "id": "phase2-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -40,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 320,
      "label": "Phase 2 — Planning (what to create?)",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 270,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## E — Cluster Discovery\n`planner.ts` · 6-stage pipeline\n\n| Stage | Source |\n|---|---|\n| 1 | SERP demand (Serper.dev) |\n| 2 | Exa semantic gap |\n| 3 | Competitor audit (LLM) |\n| 4 | News signals (14-day) |\n| 5 | GSC unmatched queries |\n| 6 | Score 0–100 + promote/dismiss |"
    },
    {
      "id": "j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 270,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "**J — Weekly Strategy**\nGap analysis +\nBrave demand\nvalidation\n→ content plan"
    },

    {
      "id": "cluster-json",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 180,
      "y": 620,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 70,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "**flagship-clusters/{slug}.json**\nCandidates → promote → targets"
    },

    {
      "id": "phase3-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -40,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 380,
      "label": "Phase 3 — Generation (two paths)",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "path1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 820,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Path 1: Reactive (D)\n`generate-seo.ts` · **daily 9 AM**\n\n**Fully automatic** gap-fill\nfrom keyword inventory\n\nTop 10 clusters (mention ≥ 2)\nMax 8 pages/run · EN + ZH\n\n**Generates:**\n- Glossary (pillar topic)\n- FAQ (brave-discussion / blog)\n- Compare (vs pattern / blog)\n- Topic Hub (mention ≥ 5)"
    },
    {
      "id": "path2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 820,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Path 2: Proactive (F)\n`generate-seo.ts --cluster`\n**Manual / on-demand**\n\n**Source-grounded** generation\nResolution: curated → Exa\n→ Brave → empty\n\n**Generates:**\n- Cornerstone (2000–4000 tok)\n- Glossary\n- FAQ\n- Compare\nMax 8 pages/run"
    },

    {
      "id": "comparison",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1240,
      "width": 680,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "### Path 1 vs Path 2\n\n| | Path 1 (Daily) | Path 2 (Cluster) |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Curation** | Fully automatic | Human-curated |\n| **Source material** | LLM knowledge only | Fetched + grounded |\n| **Scope** | Any cluster ≥ 2 mentions | Flagship topics |\n| **Quality** | Commodity SEO | Higher quality |"
    },

    {
      "id": "phase4-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -40,
      "y": 1480,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 220,
      "label": "Phase 4 — Refresh (keep content fresh)",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "g",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1530,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "**G — Detection**\nFreshness signals → page mapping\nLLM staleness check\n→ severity flags in cluster JSON"
    },
    {
      "id": "g-exec",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 1530,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "**G — Execution**\nRe-generate with fresh sources\nEN + ZH independently\nPreserves internal links"
    },

    {
      "id": "output-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -40,
